{"title_page": "Deneva Cagigas", "text_new": "{{short description|Mexican footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Deneva Cagigas\n| image          = \n| image_size     = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = Deneva Cagigas Gabilondo\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1995|04|01}}\n| birth_place    = [[Mexico City]], Mexico\n| height         = {{height|m=1.62}}\n| position       = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n| currentclub    = [[Club Universidad Nacional (Women)|UNAM]]\n| clubnumber     = 2\n| youthyears1    = \n| youthclubs1    = \n| years1         = 2017\u2013     \n| clubs1 = [[Club Universidad Nacional (Women)|UNAM]] \n| caps1 = 79\n| goals1 = 3\n| nationalyears1 = \n| nationalteam1  = \n| nationalcaps1  = \n| nationalgoals1 = \n| medaltemplates = \n| pcupdate       = 12 February 2020\n| ntupdate       = \n}}\n\n'''Deneva Cagigas Gabilondo''' (born 1 April 1995) is a Mexican professional [[association football|football]] [[defender (association football)|defender]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ligafemenil.mx/cancha/jugador/124902/eyJpZENsdWIiOiAxMTE4OH0=/deneva-cagigas-gabilondo|title=Deneva Cagigas Gabilondo\n|work=[[Liga MX Femenil]]|language=Spanish|date=|accessdate=September 30, 2017|publisher=Liga MX Femenil}}</ref> who currently plays for [[Club Universidad Nacional (Women)|UNAM]] of the [[Liga MX Femenil]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.espn.com.ar/video/clip/_/id/4880100|title=Deneva Cagigas nunca so\u00f1\u00f3 en ser profesional en su propio pa\u00eds - ESPN Video|date=2018-10-18|website=ESPN.com.ar|language=es|access-date=2020-02-13}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jornada.com.mx/2017/11/03/deportes/a11n1dep|title=La Jornada: Deneva Cagigas, de no patear un bal\u00f3n se convirti\u00f3 en la capitana de Pumas|last=C.V|first=DEMOS, Desarrollo de Medios, S. A. de|date=2017-11-03|website=www.jornada.com.mx|language=es-MX|access-date=2020-02-13}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.jornada.unam.mx/2017/11/03/deportes/a11n1dep|title=La Jornada: Deneva Cagigas, de no patear un bal\u00f3n se convirti\u00f3 en la capitana de Pumas|last=C.V.|first=DEMOS, Desarrollo de Medios, S.A. de|work=La Jornada|access-date=2018-01-08|language=es-MX}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.marca.com/claro-mx/futbol/futbol-femenil/2018/01/07/5a4fb94222601dc4498b457d.html|title=F\u00fatbol Femenil: Deneva Cagigas: \"En Pumas somos m\u00e1s maduras, m\u00e1s fuertes\" - MARCA Claro M\u00e9xico|work=MARCA Claro M\u00e9xico|access-date=2018-01-08|language=es-MX}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://toquefiltrado.com/pumas/deneva-cagigas-la-capitana-fiel-pumas/|title=Deneva Cagigas, una de las mejores capitanas|date=2017-11-29|work=Toque Filtrado|access-date=2018-01-08|language=es-ES}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.lospumasunam.com.mx/el_dia_que_deneva_cagigas_se_convirtio_en_capitana_de_pumas_femenil-noticias_de_pumas_unam-ispyp-1694478.htm|title=El d\u00eda que Deneva Cagigas se convirti\u00f3 en capitana de Pumas Femenil - La Cancha de Pumas UNAM|website=Pumas UNAM - lospumasunam.com.mx|language=es-MX|access-date=2018-01-08}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://laaficion.milenio.com/futbol/capitanas-liga_mx_femenil-monica_ocampo-cecilia_santiago-milenio-la_aficion_0_1025897447.html|title=Las voces fuertes de la Liga MX Femenil|last=Mendoza|first=Fernanda|work=Milenio|access-date=2018-01-08|language=es}}</ref>\n\n==Playing career==\nCagigas was selected as a player [[Club Universidad Nacional (Women)|UNAM]] during the inaugural season of the [[Liga MX Femenil]]. She made her debut for the club as a starter in the 2017 Apertura tournament against [[C.F. Pachuca (women)|C.F. Pachuca]]. In 2019, she captained the team.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.msn.com/es-mx/deportes/juegos-panamericanos/deneva-cagigas-la-figura-de-la-liga-mx-femenil-que-deja-huella-con-no-est%C3%A1-chido/ar-AAIxPzw|title=Deneva Cagigas, la figura de la Liga MX Femenil que deja huella con 'No Est\u00e1 Chido'|website=www.msn.com|access-date=2020-02-13}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dalepumas.bolavip.com/noticias/La-lucha-de-Deneva-Cagigas-capitana-de-Pumas-ante-las-injusticias-en-la-Liga-MX-Femenil-20190308-0005.html|title=La lucha de Deneva Cagigas, capitana de Pumas, ante las injusticias en la Liga MX Femenil|website=Dale Pumas|language=es-MX|access-date=2020-02-13}}</ref>\n\n==Other work==\nCagigas has been an ambassador for [[adidas]] since 2018.<ref>{{Citation|title=Tango League de Adidas conquist\u00f3 la CDMX|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a-jUOuHfkVU|language=en|access-date=2020-02-13}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=Entrevista con Deneva Cagigas en Tango League de Adidas|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QTsbowiJ5uk|language=en|access-date=2020-02-13}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.ligafemenil.mx/cancha/jugador/124902 Liga MX Femenil player profile]\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Cagigas, Deneva}}\n[[Category:1995 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Mexican women's footballers]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Mexico City]]\n[[Category:Mexican footballers]]\n[[Category:Liga MX Femenil players]]\n[[Category:Club Universidad Nacional (women) footballers]]\n\n\n{{Mexico-women-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Mexican footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Deneva Cagigas\n| image          = \n| image_size     = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = Deneva Cagigas Gabilondo\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1995|04|01}}\n| birth_place    = [[Mexico City]], Mexico\n| height         = {{height|m=1.62}}\n| position       = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n| currentclub    = [[Club Universidad Nacional (Women)|UNAM]]\n| clubnumber     = 2\n| youthyears1    = \n| youthclubs1    = \n| years1         = 2017\u2013     \n| clubs1 = [[Club Universidad Nacional (Women)|UNAM]] \n| caps1 = 79\n| goals1 = 3\n| nationalyears1 = \n| nationalteam1  